&lt;h1 id="think-ahead"&gt;Think ahead&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Worse than being blind, is to see and have no vision.
— Helen Keller&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is really easy to get bogged down in the details of some work and not recall the purpose of what one is actually doing; thus it is good to pause every now and then and recall &lt;strong&gt;why&lt;/strong&gt; one is pursuing a particular goal.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>